        e-mail
        chain was recorded as: &lt;injected user&gt;. </font>
    </p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">The SOC has already performed
        a preliminary investigation and determined that 2 months ago
        &lt;injected user&gt; created mailbox rules:</font></p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">&lt;rule1&gt;</font></p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">&lt;rule2&gt;</font></p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">to forward e-mails
        originating
        from &lt;affected user&gt; to the threat actor themselves. SOC
        has
        already blocked the offending e-mail, attempted to pull e-mails
        from
        inboxes of the affected individuals and, has locked the user
        account
        while also terminating any lingering sessions (O365, Mail, MFA).
      </font>
    </p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">SOC team will also review the
        following details for user: </font>
    </p>
    <p><font face="Courier New, monospace">Proxy logs to determine if a
